 Why do some feel so threatened by removal of 2 little words from a pledge which nobody is forced to say anyway? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#484848><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub97.ezboard.com/uarkuunaves.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ArkuunAves</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>NERVA Spaceplane Pilot</span><br>  Posts: 136<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(10/1/02 11:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub97.ezboard.com/fnuclearspacefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=286.topic&index=33>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Wrong, wrong, wrong.</span><hr size=1> an interesting question...<br>
